{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">This is the story of a confused little robot in an unknown future.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/steamgif1.gif?t=1736222078\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Manage A Unique Farm</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take charge of a special underground farm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Harness the unique properties of various crops to design and optimize your own efficient farm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/steamgif3.gif?t=1736222078\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect blueprints to craft items and unlock the full potential of materials.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover and capture a wide variety of fish, each with unique functions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mine for ores to upgrade your permanent abilities and enhance your progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/steamgif4.gif?t=1736222078\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/B0714007937511D42F9920AE1ACE0A76.png?t=1736222078\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore The World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a journey to uncover the truth about the world\u2014and yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003050/extras/steamgif2.gif?t=1736222078\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Traverse paths to unlock new areas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Encounter a wide range of robot friends\u2014or foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solve tasks and tackle challenging problems as you progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared